      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a dependable ride with plenty of life left? This vehicle is in fair condition and is ready for its next adventure! It shows some honest signs of use and character, making it a fantastic, budget-friendly option for someone looking for a solid daily driver. With a little bit of love, this car will continue to serve you well for miles to come!",
