    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a reliable daily driver for someone willing to address a few minor issues. The exterior shows its age with some noticeable scratches, a small dent on the rear passenger door, and some fading on the plastic trim. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, though the suspension is starting to feel soft and it will likely need new brakes in the near future. The interior is generally clean but shows typical wear on the driver's seat and carpet. It has been a dependable car, but it is no longer in peak aesthetic or mechanical shape.",
