    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair, honest condition and serves as a reliable daily driver. While it remains mechanically sound, the exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, minor door dings, and some fading on the clear coat. Inside, the upholstery has some visible wear and a few stains, though it remains comfortable. It has been regularly serviced, but a new owner should expect to address some minor cosmetic issues and typical wear-and-tear items in the near future. This is a solid, functional car for someone looking for dependable transportation at an affordable price point.",
